SEARCH
Package Server.Models

Class Book

java.lang.Object
Server.Models.Book
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Book extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a book with details such as ISBN, title, author, editor, language, release year, and borrow count. This class implements Serializable to allow book objects to be serialized.
